        "created_at": "2021-05-03T05:51:12.996Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"amirouche\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"2685\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://sea1.discourse-cdn.com/foundationdb/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/amirouche/48/1911_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> amirouche:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Since <a href=\"https://apple.github.io/foundationdb/javadoc/com/apple/foundationdb/FDB.html#createCluster-java.lang.String-\">createCluster </a> is deprecated, it is not possible anymore to connect to two different FDB clusters from the same POSIX processus.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You can use <code>FDB.open()</code> multiple times in the same process to connect to different clusters.</p>",
